        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Junia AI vs Writesonic — which is better?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Writesonic has more polish, broader template library, and better integrations. Junia has built-in autoblogging, bulk generation modes, and SEO-focused workflows out of the box. Pick Writesonic for marketing copy; pick Junia for high-volume blog/SEO content." }},
